    conversation_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID NOT NULL,
    message_text TEXT NOT NULL,
    timestamp TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE ChatbotConversations (
  conversation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  bot_id INT,
  message TEXT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE chatbot_conversations (
	conversation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	user_id INT,
	bot_id INT,
	timestamp TIMESTAMP,
	message TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE users (
	user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	username VARCHAR(50),
	email VARCHAR(100),
	age INT,
	gender VARCHAR(10)
)

CREATE TABLE bots (
	bot_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	bot_name VARCHAR(50),
	language VARCHAR(20),
	version FLOAT,
	created_at DATE
)

CREATE TABLE messages (
	message_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	conversation_id INT,
	sender_id INT,
	message_text TEXT,
	timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE ratings (
	rating_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	conversation_id INT,
	rating INT,
	comment TEXT,
	created_at DATE
)
